  "remarks": "JSC Design Bureau of Instrument-Making Named After Academic A. G. Shipunov (JSC KBP) is one of the oldest enterprises in the Russian defence complex. It develops a wide variety of heavy military equipment including Kornet anti-tank weapons, Krasnopol missiles, and Tunguska and Pantsir-S1 anti-aircraft systems. JSC KBP belongs to the Russian state corporation Rostec.",
